                                                                                int steerEncoderPort,
                                                                                double steerOffset)
        Creates a Mk4 swerve module that uses Falcon 500s for driving and steering. Module information is displayed in the specified ShuffleBoard container.
        Parameters:
        container - The container to display module information in.
        configuration - Module configuration parameters to use.
        gearRatio - The gearing configuration the module is in.
        driveMotorPort - The CAN ID of the drive Falcon 500.
        steerMotorPort - The CAN ID of the steer Falcon 500.
        steerEncoderPort - The CAN ID of the steer CANCoder.
        steerOffset - The offset of the CANCoder in radians.
        Returns:
        The configured swerve module.
